      • ConvertSpeed

        public static double ConvertSpeed(int from,
                                  int to,
                                  double value)
        Returns a value that has been converted from one speed unit to another as a double. This method should only be used to convert speed units. If other units are used, method will simply return the original parameter value.
        Parameters:
        from - an int specifying what unit to convert from.
        to - an int specifying what unit to convert to.
        value - an int/double for what value the user wishes to convert.
        Returns:
        double value that has been converted from one unit to another.
